title: Launch Partner: Enya.ai
body:
#### Proposal overview
Enya.ai recently signed our Memo of Understanding (MOU).  This proposal is to accept/deny them as a Web3API launch partner.  Learn more about them [here](https://www.enya.ai/company/about).

#### Github pull request: 
👉 [Enya.ai signed MOU #149](https://github.com/Web3-API/dao/pull/149).
